Thank you for using the Color Suggestion Extension. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a safe online experience. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our extension.

Information We Collect
The Color Suggestion Extension does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users. We respect your privacy and are committed to ensuring that your data remains private and secure.

Usage Data
We may collect anonymous usage data to help improve the functionality and performance of the extension. This data includes information such as:

The frequency of use of the extension
The styles selected by users
This information is collected in an aggregated form and cannot be used to identify individual users.

How We Use the Information
The information we collect is used solely for the following purposes:

To improve and optimize the extension
To understand usage patterns and preferences
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside parties your personally identifiable information.

Data Security
We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

Third-Party Services
The Color Suggestion Extension does not integrate with or provide any personal data to third-party services.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

By using the Color Suggestion Extension, you consent to our Privacy Policy.

